	    <section class="slider__item" id="progetti0" data-path="/fable" >
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="cont">
                <div class="grid-50 first">
                    <div class="mask-rect mask-rect--left">
                        <img class="clipped" src="../../assets/images/progetti/favola-small.jpg" />
                    </div>
                    <h2>
                        <span>Petas: discover </span><span>the magic</span>
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-50">
                    <div class="cont-text right-text">
                        <p>After the success gained at Expo Milan 2015, Petas realized all the new thematic decorations for the new Gardaland Resort, the Adventure Hotel, and all the scenography for the new Park’s ride: the Kung Fu Panda Academy.</p>
                        <p class="text-simple">Fiberglass scenography, decorations and sculptures brought to life a unique Hotel, dedicated to the bravest adventurers that, due to the four themed Rooms (Jungle, Arabian, Artic and Wild West), can challenge themselves during their stay.
The Restaurant’s decorations, inspired by Tutankhamon’s Legend, offer a real journey through the Ancient Egypt;
guests can undertake this journey since entering the building’s threshold, walking through the Submarine. 
The Kung Fu Panda Academy symbolizes Petas perfect achievement in the reproduction of Dreamworks Magic World:  each detail and every single aspect deeply follows the famous animation movie.</p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="no-link open-overlay" data-overlay-id="gallery" data-section="dreamworks"><span> project </span></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="slider__item" id="progetti1" data-path="/expo">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="cont">

                <div class="grid-50 grid-right">
					<div class="mask-rect mask-rect--right">
						<img class="clipped" src="../../assets/images/progetti/childrenpark_small.jpg" />
					</div>
					<h2>
						<span>Petas for</span><span>Expo</span>
					</h2>
                </div>

                <div class="grid-50 grid-left">
                    <div class="cont-text left-text">
                        <p>Petas brings fun, educational and relaxing areas for children to the one of the most important international projects – EXPO Milan 2015.</p>
                        <p class="text-simple">This amazing multicultural exhibition is designed and organized around child and family-friendly approach to welcome visitors of all ages. The theme "Feeding the Planet, Energy for Life” is interpreted through interactive spaces based on play and discovery of different forms of life on the planet. The EXPO Children Park allows small adventurers exploring all the earth’s key elements such as water, air, land, energy and flora & fauna in an engaging, joyful and amusing way. It’s about a powerful message delivered in a powerful setting.</p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="no-link open-overlay" data-overlay-id="gallery" data-section="expo"><span> project </span></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
